Package com.epam.jwd.task01.logic

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComparatorStonesByPrice
    A comparison function, which uses values of the field stonePrice in instances of Gemstone
    GemstoneListCreator
    Base method to create and add into list GemstoneList instances of Gemstone Each GemstoneList is based on Arraylist collection and able to use all relevant methods.
    JewelsInfoPrinter
    Utility class, containing only: a) methods for console output of GemstoneListCreator GemstoneList and NecklaceCreator Necklace, which both are instances of ArrayList collection and able to use all relevant methods; b) methods for console output of NecklaceCalculator methods for current Necklace instance.
    NecklaceCalculator
    Utility class, containing only methods for calculating NecklaceCreator Necklace instances total cost and weight.
    NecklaceCreator
    Base method to add into list Necklace instances of Gemstone from source list GemstoneList Each Necklace is based on Arraylist collection and able to use all relevant methods.
    NecklaceSortAndFilterMaker
    Utility class containing only methods for sorting and filtering of elements Gemstone in NecklaceCreator Necklace No instances of this class can exist, and all its fields and methods are static.
